Before scouring the net to find whatever third party app you can install,
review what comes native with your OS for applicability.
Windows - bitlocker
FreeBSD - geli
Linux - dm-crypt
MacOS - filevault
etc...

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Comparison_of_disk_encryption_software

